{"tid":1912954,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"港台跪低講支那衰野外購紀錄片都提早下架","createTime":"2020-03-06T12:28:14.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-08T07:13:32.000Z","uid":49359,"like":103,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":49,"replies":[{"pid":"679e6667f48760475b8922564501e0d77fe73ce5","tid":1912954,"uid":49359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T12:28:14.000Z","msg":"都係31看世界節目<br />\n西藏優化工程<br />\n講支那打壓西藏宗教自由<br />\n無提供網上直播<br />\n我唔肯定係提早下架<br />\n但正常都有2個星期網上重播<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.rthk.hk/tv/dtt31/programme/31seetheworld/episode/620156\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rthk.hk%2Ftv%2Fdtt31%2Fprogramme%2F31seetheworld%2Fepisode%2F620156&d=%2FrzxgVsCSRBeEmt1flTkcFe0bVP%2BLlUkdLfYKyPPBhg%3D&h=5aabcdc1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.rthk.hk/tv/dtt31/programme/31seetheworld/episode/620156</a><br />\n<br />\n今個星期套中國世紀工程<br />\n講一帶一路當地人不滿<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.rthk.hk/tv/dtt31/programme/31seetheworld/episode/622399\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rthk.hk%2Ftv%2Fdtt31%2Fprogramme%2F31seetheworld%2Fepisode%2F622399&d=%2FrzxgVsCSRBeEmt1flTkcFe0bVP%2BLlUkdLfYKyPPBhg%3D&h=fa4acf50\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.rthk.hk/tv/dtt31/programme/31seetheworld/episode/622399</a><br />\n我有開POST<br />\n我叫人睇直播<br />\n因為我覺上次係有人停左網上重搵<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1910160/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1910160/page/1</a><br />\n當晚直播完<br />\n我就立刻睇有無重播<br />\n我見網上重搵係到出年<br />\n但今日再睇已經無網上重搵<br />\n可以證實有人打壓<br />\n今日將講支那醜聞節目下架<br />\n以後係唔係唔可以買支那醜聞節目<br />\n到時31看世界變31看支那"},{"pid":"3f28ca0af23fcac0a6eb0cfa83cc02753fcc2620","tid":1912954,"uid":49359,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T12:32:09.000Z","msg":"今日仲有人講套野<br />\n<br />\n[RTHK][31 看世界]中國世紀工程<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1912452/page/1#preview\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1912452/page/1#preview</a><br />\n證明係岩岩先下架"},{"pid":"c39ba288fe6586d74bb7db571c82067a7fd16e61","tid":1912954,"uid":2526,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T12:33:27.000Z","msg":"全港市民撐都跪<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a4a694557dc1bbbd6fc0ec0956739dbeb464be6","tid":1912954,"uid":49359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T12:36:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d9265e097040cc8bb835c1e6e56ee492eb27a38","tid":1912954,"uid":49359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T12:37:10.000Z","msg":"幾時會到頭條新聞"},{"pid":"b0c031bb0c4f122f555817b2dd76b56f8726acf2","tid":1912954,"uid":77416,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T12:37:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ec4046437446921b0e8cecef38622c97d728c0a","tid":1912954,"uid":228955,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T12:37:31.000Z","msg":"所以幾時支持返港台呢完全冇人行動"},{"pid":"6379a227866af4dee250b82623fd41f91487ee85","tid":1912954,"uid":49955,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T12:37:55.000Z","msg":"版權買番黎有限制？"},{"pid":"d2138d942bce3c9d0218f0b9bfa6e44cd27545f9","tid":1912954,"uid":49359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6379a227866af4dee250b82623fd41f91487ee85","tid":1912954,"uid":49955,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T12:37:55.000Z","msg":"版權買番黎有限制？"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T12:44:05.000Z","msg":"通常港台買返黎都有一年到2個星期網上重溫"},{"pid":"72333ebe168dda86fa73e30bfeed0bd7c7d12b24","tid":1912954,"uid":53003,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T12:46:11.000Z","msg":"屌！港台啲記錄片真係好撚高汁"},{"pid":"56adda281692a4